  "title": "Associate HR Manager / Assistant HR Manager #79249",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacture of special purpose machinery</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Senior HR Executive / Assistant HR Manager</strong></li><li>Working Location: Woodlands</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday-Friday, 8.30am - 5.45pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Transport allowance + VB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead full-cycle recruitment and onboarding.</li><li>Manage end-to-end work pass processes (applications, renewals, cancellations).</li><li>Develop and implement HR policies, procedures, and HRIS workflows.</li><li>Drive engagement, training, and performance management initiatives.</li><li>Handle employee relations, including investigations, disciplinary actions, and conflict resolution.</li><li>Maintain accurate HRIS and personnel records; ensure compliance with labor laws and company policies.</li><li>Support payroll and benefits; administer time & attendance and leave, coordinating with payroll.</li><li>Assist on any ad‑hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or higher in HR, Business Administration, or related field.</li><li>3–5 years of HR experience, manufacturing environment preferred.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79249 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
